 trying to find the exit.\n\nSwing your arms down to stretch the bandage, grab the gimmick with the bandage and jump.\nThe realistic VR and high-speed movement are exhilarating and it feels good.\nOnce you get the hang of it, you will come to know the fun of the game.\n\n* Stretching bandage\n* High speed jump movement\n* Climbing the wall / Trapeze\n* Trap that blocks the way\n* Various game stages\n* The rank of clearing the stage\n\nThe video and screenshots were taken with Quest2.", "short_description": "A mummy girl who has been asleep deep inside a pyramid for more than 1000 years wakes up.\nShe doesn\u2019t know what era is it is, who she is, or the reason she's there.\nShe keeps walking, trying to find the exit."}]}, "developer_name": "\u307e\u3053\u3061\u3083\u3093\u3068\u3044\u3063\u3057\u3087", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.withmako.com/VRMummyGirl_PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "\u307e\u3053\u3061\u3083\u3093\u3068\u3044\u3063\u3057\u3087", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.withmako.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["ja", "en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "5263033140376304"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1074533903404723"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1074533903404723"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {